      <title>0.2.2</title>
      <pubDate>Sat, 19 Jul 2026 08:50:00 +0900</pubDate>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.4</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>Groovyday 0.2.2</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Update checks now run at every launch (previously only once a day), so new releases are noticed right away</li>
          <li>Full app menu inside the window: hover the mode-switcher or right-click the visualizer for Settings, Check for Updates, and Quit — works even when the menu bar icon is hidden by the MacBook notch</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
